Release Notes - nfsroot-1.7                                 15 Sep 2006
=======================================================================

* mklivecd is provided to convert an nfsroot-enabled root image into
  a ``livecd'' ISO image.

* Boot failure in the initrd will result in a debug shell rather than
  the old ``fix the world'' message.

